{"tid":390841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】深潛後升水過急 漁夫慘變「米芝蓮人」","createTime":"2017-09-07T10:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T11:06:24.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af0bf25856346aba994fefdafc79b04d3ff841b6","tid":390841,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170906/large/1504688676_9291.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170906%2Flarge%2F1504688676_9291.jpg&h=45553970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170906/large/1504688677_8bae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170906%2Flarge%2F1504688677_8bae.jpg&h=f8bfa72f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024/201611/20161101094539_0_13938374_1564678293840254_6694003219968683923_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024%2F201611%2F20161101094539_0_13938374_1564678293840254_6694003219968683923_n.jpg&h=23061891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n秘魯一名男子打魚期間，潛落水底後急速升上水面，出現俗稱潛水夫病（Diver's disease）的減壓症（Decompression sickness）。他的身體脹大變形，慘成「米芝蓮人」，他走路出現困難，更要忍受極大痛楚。<br />\n<br />\n馬丁尼斯（Alejandro Ramos Martinez）早前潛到海底捉海產，上水後雙臂及胸口肌肉突然暴脹，體重足足增加近32公斤，原來是患上減壓症。減壓症症狀包括皮膚痕癢、頭痛、意識模糊、關節疼痛、惡心及嘔吐等。當人體潛下深水地方時壓力較大，令氮氣溶解於血液；當人體急速升上水面，壓力紓緩，血液內的氮氣便會形成大量氣泡，有機會引致血管栓塞，嚴重者甚至可以致命。<br />\n<br />\n馬丁尼斯體內氮氣形成的大氣泡出現在肌肉周圍，情況屬於特殊。他患病後非常疼痛而且走路有困難，亦因而患上嚴重高血壓，目前正在加壓室接受氧氣治療，主治醫生及醫療團隊已經幫他將30%的氮氣排出體外。醫生說雖然曾考慮開刀排出氮氣，但擔心手術太高難度而作罷。<br />\n<br />\n隨着科技進步，減壓症已經越來越少發生，現時潛水員可以用潛水錶來計算他們升上水面的速度，令他們可以慢慢升上水面、逐步減壓，以避免減壓症發生。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》／《蘋果》資料室  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170907/57175582\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170907%2F57175582&d=Q3kjnObNMURrvSdCA%2Bi%2BKv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=0324afec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170907%2F57175582&h=46b06da0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170907/57175582</a>"},{"pid":"de6df5fb0db89f582987a9a3dc80666d4415aa9a","tid":390841,"uid":28619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:47:44.000Z","msg":"咁都唔死得"},{"pid":"74aee98e88879a61e9910f955205bf22dffe23b2","tid":390841,"uid":31002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:48:41.000Z","msg":"屌，忍唔到笑，好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c15e56542d37d6c70e9b9080b85837a20577dbd","tid":390841,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:49:37.000Z","msg":"鯊海47米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係講深潛唔可以一野上返水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10fc4b208132dd87eea32a1128cc8a754be1dba","tid":390841,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.lailasblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/06063215/optimized-bjyj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.lailasblog.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F06063215%2Foptimized-bjyj.jpg&h=5803c5bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇到都覺得恐怖<br />\n好驚佢爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2debf8086ecdf733d9647a63dbea56f72120e465","tid":390841,"uid":46933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:54:31.000Z","msg":"諗下裡面果d係水泡就覺得好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8372f55112f47d