kquote>四檔路飛？</blockquote><br />\n用完要潛水十分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n然後上水再變四檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}